{"sn15.10:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 15.10 ","sn15.10:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn15.10:0.3":"Puggalasutta ","sn15.10:1.1":"Ekam samayam bhagava rajagahe viharati gijjhakute pabbate. ","sn15.10:1.2":"Tatra kho bhagava bhikkhu amantesi: ","sn15.10:1.3":"“bhikkhavo”ti. ","sn15.10:1.4":"“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","sn15.10:1.5":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","sn15.10:2.1":"“Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro …pe… ","sn15.10:2.2":"ekapuggalassa, bhikkhave, kappam sandhavato samsarato siya evam maha atthikankalo atthipunjo atthirasi yathayam vepullo pabbato, sace samharako assa, sambhatanca na vinasseyya. ","sn15.10:2.3":"Tam kissa hetu? ","sn15.10:2.4":"Anamataggoyam, bhikkhave, samsaro …pe… ","sn15.10:2.5":"alam vimuccitun”ti. ","sn15.10:3.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn15.10:3.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn15.10:4.1":"“Ekassekena kappena, ","sn15.10:4.2":"puggalassatthisancayo; ","sn15.10:4.3":"Siya pabbatasamo rasi, ","sn15.10:4.4":"iti vuttam mahesina. ","sn15.10:5.1":"So kho panayam akkhato, ","sn15.10:5.2":"vepullo pabbato maha; ","sn15.10:5.3":"Uttaro gijjhakutassa, ","sn15.10:5.4":"magadhanam giribbaje. ","sn15.10:6.1":"Yato ca ariyasaccani, ","sn15.10:6.2":"sammappannaya passati; ","sn15.10:6.3":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","sn15.10:6.4":"dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","sn15.10:6.5":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","sn15.10:6.6":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","sn15.10:7.1":"Sa sattakkhattumparamam, ","sn15.10:7.2":"sandhavitvana puggalo; ","sn15.10:7.3":"Dukkhassantakaro hoti, ","sn15.10:7.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhaya”ti. ","sn15.10:7.5":"Dasamam. ","sn15.10:7.6":"Pathamo vaggo. ","sn15.10:8.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn15.10:8.1":"Tinakatthanca pathavi, ","sn15.10:8.2":"assu khiranca pabbatam; ","sn15.10:8.3":"Sasapa savaka ganga, ","sn15.10:8.4":"dando ca puggalena cati. "}